cs.HC, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SY. 

This paper focuses on human-robot interaction and the design of control and feedback interfaces for better collaboration between humans and machines. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). The paper also involves reinforcement learning and robotics, which suggests the categories cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also presents experimental results and a learning framework, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
